96%9A%E6%83%85%E6%84%9F%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E8%8D%AF/</link><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2020 23:40:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB134-%E5%86%85%E7%96%9A%E6%83%85%E6%84%9F%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E8%8D%AF/</guid><description>当我们违反了个人标准，确实会有一种令人困扰的情绪萦绕我们，但它从本质上讲是一种遗憾，而不是罪恶感。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻133-丧失：与精神创伤带伤前进</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB133-%E4%B8%A7%E5%A4%B1%E4%B8%8E%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%88%9B%E4%BC%A4%E5%B8%A6%E4%BC%A4%E5%89%8D%E8%BF%9B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2020 22:54:22 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB133-%E4%B8%A7%E5%A4%B1%E4%B8%8E%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%88%9B%E4%BC%A4%E5%B8%A6%E4%BC%A4%E5%89%8D%E8%BF%9B/</guid><description>人类最重要的前进动力之一，就是寻找人生经历的意义。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻132-孤独：人际关系的“肌无力”</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB132-%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%85%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%82%8C%E6%97%A0%E5%8A%9B/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2020 23:31:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB132-%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%85%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%82%8C%E6%97%A0%E5%8A%9B/</guid><description>拥有有意义的人际关系，是过上快乐和自我实现的生活的关键，长期的孤独则会损害我们最基本的快乐。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻131-拒绝：情绪伤害</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB131-%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2020 23:41:06 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91/2020-05-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB131-%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3/</guid><description>拒绝引起的情绪痛苦是如此的尖锐，以至于影响到我们的思想，让我们充满愤怒，削弱我们的自信和自尊，动摇我们最基本的归属感。</description></item></channel></rss>